sentences.english: The football player was built like a moose.

sentences.english: The moose turned and charged straight into the dog team.
sentences.chinese: 驼鹿转身向着狗队扑了上来。

sentences.english: Moose may not be viewed from an airplane.

sentences.english: The only tracks were those made by bears, wolves, elk and moose.
